<div class='success'>Thanks for shopping at our store! Come back soon!</div>
The Pet Palace is a great place to find just the right animal companion.  The owners, Frank and Rosie Ruiz, are animal-lovers and are very eager to find good homes for all of the animals in their shop.  They're always willing to explain the responsibilities and joys of pet ownership to interested customers, as well as offering tips on animal care.  So, whether you'd like a more traditional friend, like a dog or a cat, or a strange and exotic animal, like a sugar glider or an iguana, you're sure to find the perfect pet for your lifestyle at The Pet Palace.<br><br>Don't forget though, in addition to getting your new pet here, make sure to pick up food and any other supplies you may need... including a toy or two! You definitely want your new friend to feel happy and welcome into their new home! You can browse different kinds of items by clicking them above.<div align='center'><table align='center' border='0' cellpadding='0' cellspacing='0'><tr>
